description: Soaring 11 ft high ceilings, prime location, situated within the historic Monks Building on West Broadway. This corner 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is southeast facing, featuring brilliant natural sunlight and stunning wide-plank hardwood floors throughout, creating a unique and calming ambiance. On the west side of Southie, walking distance to the Broadway T stop and #9 bus, this unit is close to all the best nightlife, dining, and shopping in the area. Just around the corner, Loco, Lincoln, Broadway and Playwright are waiting. This spacious condo makes for the quintessential Boston home. Parking is street/permit parking. Extra large storage cage included.
